Hey David,

I'm glad to hear you're back. I'd like to check in on how the AIC is doing - previously we were getting a 500 error when searching users in the AIC and trying to use the reports within. That was cleared up in AIC v11.6.0.36+ so patching to a build post-that should correct your issue. Let me know once you've had time to update, or if you need any assistance doing so.

Thank you,
